Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,AI video technology is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.41,0:00:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,revolutionizing the way we
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.81,0:00:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,create and consume content.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.55,0:00:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, advancements in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.87,0:00:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,machine learning and computer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.05,0:00:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,vision are at the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.01,0:00:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,forefront,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.75,0:00:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,allowing for incredible innovations
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.33,0:00:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,such as deep fakes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and automated editing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,These technologies are not
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.25,0:00:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,just fascinating, they're reshaping
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the landscape of digital
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.19,0:00:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,media as we know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.44,0:00:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,At the core of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.07,0:00:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,AI video advancements, lies
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,generative, adversarial networks, or
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.39,0:00:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,GANs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,These networks are crucial
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,for creating synthetic video
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.12,0:00:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,content
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that feels authentic and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.14,0:00:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,improves quality dramatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that, but
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,AI tools are streamlining
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,video editing processes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,allowing creators to produce
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.82,0:00:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,content faster and unleash
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.67,0:00:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,their creativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine watching a live
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.79,0:00:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,stream where the video
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.57,0:00:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,quality is dynamically adjusted
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.24,0:00:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,in real time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.20,0:00:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is possible thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to AI algorithms that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.25,0:00:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,enhance video quality on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.60,0:00:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Coupled with AI -driven
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.21,0:00:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,analytics, content creators can
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,gain insights into viewer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Optimizing content based on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:00:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,actual data.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Personalization is another game
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.03,0:00:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,changer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:01:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,AI can generate content
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.07,0:01:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,tailored to user preferences
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and viewing history.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This means that every
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,viewer can have a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.64,0:01:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,unique experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Additionally, AI plays a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.45,0:01:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,vital role in making
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.56,0:01:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,videos accessible
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.59,0:01:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,through automatic captioning and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,translation,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,breaking down barriers for
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,a global audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.70,0:01:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what does the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,future hold for AI
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.56,0:01:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,in video?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.31,0:01:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The integration of augmented
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.50,0:01:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,our and virtual reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.90,0:01:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We are technologies promises
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.12,0:01:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to create truly immersive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that will redefine storytelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.21,0:01:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,With the rise of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,virtual influencers and AI
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.71,0:01:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-enhanced live streaming,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the possibilities are endless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.06,0:01:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Embracing AI in video
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.51,0:01:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,production isn't just a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,trend,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the future of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.87,0:01:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,content creation.
